### List all channels
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels

### Get channel by ID (Video)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/1

### Get channel by ID (Display)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/2

### Get channel by ID (Social)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/3

### Get channel by code
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/code/VIDEO

### Get channel by code (lowercase - should work)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/code/display

### Get non-existent channel by ID (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/999

### Get non-existent channel by code (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/channels/code/UNKNOWN
